p.span: (IC-1) The IVM' serial number must be unique.

div.p: (IC-2) The name of the Retailer must be unique.
(IC-3) The EAN must be a 13 digits integer.
(IC-4) A category can only belong to 1 super-category.
(IC-5) A category cannot be a super-category of itself.
(IC-6) Each retailer must only replenish one category for each IVM.
(IC-7) The Shelf's number must be unique for each IVM.
(IC-8) The TIN must be a 9 digits integer.
